<!DOCTYPE html><html lang="en"><head><meta charset="utf-8"/><meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1"/><title>Launching Soon | Build With AI Enterprise</title><meta name="description" content="Sovereign, AI-native infrastructure for Web2/Web3 teams. Launching June 14, 2026."/></head><body style="margin:0;padding:2rem;font-family:system-ui;background:#0A0F1A;color:#fff;text-align:center"><h1 style="font-size:clamp(2rem,5vw,3.5rem);margin-bottom:1rem"><span style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,#22d3ee,#3b82f6,#a855f7);-webkit-background-clip:text;-webkit-text-fill-color:transparent">Build With AI</span><br/><span style="color:#fff">Enterprise Dev OS</span></h1><p style="color:#9ca3af;font-size:1.125rem;max-width:42rem;margin:0 auto 2rem">Launching June 14, 2026. Sovereign AI-native infrastructure for Web2/Web3 teams.</p><div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(4,1fr);gap:1rem;max-width:28rem;margin:0 auto"><div style="background:#111827;border:1px solid #374151;border-radius:1rem;padding:1.25rem"><span style="font-size:1.75rem;font-weight:700" id="d">00</span><br/><span style="font-size:.75rem;text-transform:uppercase;color:#9ca3af">Days</span></div><div style="background:#111827;border:1px solid #374151;border-radius:1rem;padding:1.25rem"><span style="font-size:1.75rem;font-weight:700" id="h">00</span><br/><span style="font-size:.75rem;text-transform:uppercase;color:#9ca3af">Hours</span></div><div style="background:#111827;border:1px solid #374151;border-radius:1rem;padding:1.25rem"><span style="font-size:1.75rem;font-weight:700" id="m">00</span><br/><span style="font-size:.75rem;text-transform:uppercase;color:#9ca3af">Minutes</span></div><div style="background:#111827;border:1px solid #374151;border-radius:1rem;padding:1.25rem"><span style="font-size:1.75rem;font-weight:700" id="s">00</span><br/><span style="font-size:.75rem;text-transform:uppercase;color:#9ca3af">Seconds</span></div></div><script>const L=new Date('2026-06-14T00:00:00Z');function u(){const d=L-Date.now();if(d<=0)return;document.getElementById('d').textContent=String(Math.floor(d/864e5)).padStart(2,'0');document.getElementById('h').textContent=String(Math.floor(d%864e5/36e5)%24).padStart(2,'0');document.getElementById('m').textContent=String(Math.floor(d%36e5/6e4)%60).padStart(2,'0');document.getElementById('s').textContent=String(Math.floor(d%6e4/1e3)%60).padStart(2,'0')}u();setInterval(u,1e3)</script></body></html>